</article>
<article class="reading-list-item">
<div class='sections' style='color: #0ba864;'>Environment &amp; Health</div>
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/a-covid-19-vaccine-will-not-be-enough-we-need-a-plan-to-distribute-it/">A COVID-19 Vaccine Will Not Be Enough &#8212; We Need a Plan to Distribute It</a>
</article>
</div>
</aside>
