<article class="row hentry post-269169 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-op-ed tag-california tag-coronavirus tag-covid-19 tag-health-care tag-ohio tag-paid-sick-leave tag-pandemic tag-texas section-politics-and-elections primary_topic-politics" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ReportageNewsArticle">
