</span></h3>
<div class="row">
<p class="hellobar-description"><span class="show-for-medium">When it comes to waging war, stripping basic rights, election fraud, or a global health crisis, there is no such thing as "alternative facts." Choose media that's been exposing government and corporate exploitation since day one: <b>Donate now to help us raise the $36,000 we need to keep publishing fearless journalism.</b></span>
